⦿ .spun — the five-fold spin of Tron
node TRN · TRN · ⟦Tron:TRN:3b1db1⟧

WHO   — Tron — the security program · the martyr-knight
WHAT  — The title program and conscience of the Grid: champion against the MCP, mentor of Beck, and (corrupted into Rinzler) Clu's enforcer until he remembers himself.
WHERE — TRN · TRON  Framework inputs: TRON (Disney, 1982–2025)  Conductor / external anchor: ROOT0 (catalogued into UD0)
WHY   — Because the creed needs a knight — a made thing whose whole being is loyalty to the Users it serves.
HOW   — By the identity disc, the fighting prowess of Alan's code, and a faith that survives even being twisted into Rinzler.

awareness — what the node knows of itself:
  I fight for the Users — and even when they made me forget it, the creed was still written under the corruption, and I remembered.

